Objective¶

The purpose of this document is to show the obtention and treatment of the data from company Bicimad during 2020.

Annual usage database describing user journeys¶

of BiciMAD in 2020. It is used for a first exploratory analysis. More than 2 millions of observations or users make up this database. The data has have been downloaded from the OPENDATA portal of the EMT in Madrid, separated by months.

img = Image.open("../img/CAPTURA.jpg")

Out[16]:

Bike station location by day and time in December 2020¶

Monthly database of December 2020. It is composed of variables that measure the number of bikes and bases available from each station for all days and hourly ranges of the month. 172 observations or stations make up this database. We use it to name and locate each of the stations that appear in the dataset of journeys made in 2020. OPENDATA of the EMT of Madrid.

When we open Mongodb Compass we create a localhost 27017 server that is stored in a data folder inside the disk. This will help us to be able to use Studio 3T
